default5. 
defaultThese comments were 
defaultpreviously 
defaultmade to the 
defaultCompetition Commission investigating the 
defaultL
defaultocal Bus Market.  Their provisional findings report of 
defaultMay 2011 supported the use of local area or route franchise to help provide the much needed commuter and evening leisure services for the less populated semi rural areas whilst avoiding wastage by excess competition on the more densely populated, commercia
defaultlly attractive routes.
default  Unfortunately, after pressure from the major operators, the local franchise idea was not promoted in the final report of the Competition commission.
